description: The list of test set executions.

parameters.name: sortBy
parameters.description: The sort order of the test set executions. Specifies whether to sort the test set executions by the date and time at which the test sets were created. Specifies whether to sort in ascending or descending order.

nested_params.name: attribute
nested_params.description: Specifies whether to sort the test set executions by the date and time at which the test sets were created.

nested_params.name: order
nested_params.description: Specifies whether to sort in ascending or descending order.

nested_items.name: testExecutionId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the test execution.

nested_items.name: creationDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time at which the test execution was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time at which the test execution was last updated.

nested_items.name: testExecutionStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the test execution.

nested_items.name: testSetId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the test set used in the test execution.

nested_items.name: testSetName
nested_items.description: The name of the test set used in the test execution.

nested_items.name: botAliasTarget
nested_items.description: Contains information about the bot alias used for the test execution.

nested_items.name: botId
nested_items.description: The bot Id of the bot alias used in the test set execution.

nested_items.name: botAliasId
nested_items.description: The bot alias Id of the bot alias used in the test set execution.

nested_items.name: localeId
nested_items.description: The locale Id of the bot alias used in the test set execution.

nested_items.name: apiMode
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the API mode for the test execution is streaming or non-streaming.

nested_items.name: testExecutionModality
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the data used for the test execution is written or spoken.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates whether there are more results to return in a response to the ListTestExecutions operation. If the nextToken field is present, you send the contents as the nextToken parameter of a ListTestExecutions operation request to get the next page of results.
